Path
- Path&#x3D;&#x2F;gate&#x2F;,&#x2F;rule&#x2F;
## 当请求的路径为gate、rule开头的时，转发到http://localhost:9023服务器上


Before
- Before&#x3D;2017-01-20T17:42:47.789-07:00[America&#x2F;Denver]
